# Code Modification (The Game Shelf)

Grounded in how this repo actually works. For adding a game end-to-end, use `.cursor/skills/add-game/SKILL.md`. For new trainer types, use `.claude/skills/add-trainer` + `docs/trainer-system.md`. After verify, follow `verify-then-push.mdc`.

## Layers (do not blur)

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `content/games/` | **Source of truth** for games (`index.json`, `meta.json`, `en\|zh/rules.md`, root `flow.json` / `score.json` / `trainer.json` / `calculator.json`) |
| `src/` | App Router UI, domain libs, types |
| `public/data/` | **Generated** by `prebuild` (`games-meta.json`, `rules/<slug>.json`, `cover-manifest.json`) — not a hand-edit source of truth |
| `scripts/` | Only lifecycle hooks: `generate-game-data` (prebuild), `generate-sw-precache` + `generate-seo` (postbuild). Keep `generate-icons.mjs` for icon regen; do not revive one-off scripts |

Static export (`output: "export"`, `basePath: "/boardgames"`, `trailingSlash: true`): **no** API routes, middleware, or runtime Node server features.

## Data loading

- **Pages (server)**: `GameRepository` / `GameFactory` + `params: Promise<…>` + `generateStaticParams`. Do not invent a parallel fs/fetch path for content.
- **Client runtime fetch** (chat, covers): always prefix `/boardgames/…`. Covers use `cover-manifest.json` only — never multi-extension `<img>` probing.
- **Do not** reintroduce monolithic `games-index.json`. Chat uses `games-meta.json` + `rules/<slug>.json`.

## Server vs client

- Keep `src/app/[locale]/**/page.tsx` as **Server Components**. Put `"use client"` on interactive pieces under `src/components/`, not on whole game pages just for hooks.
- Feature pages: config exists in content → `generateStaticParams` filters → page branches on `type` → client component.

## i18n (as used today)

- UI chrome → `messages/en.json` + `messages/zh.json` via `useTranslations` in client components.
- Game content bilingual fields → `{ "en", "zh" }` inside `meta` / `flow` / `score` / `trainer` JSON.
- Server pages often use `locale === "zh" ? … : …` or `meta.name[locale]`.
- Links: `next/link` + `` `/${locale}/…/` `` (trailing slash). Do **not** assume `@/i18n/navigation` or `getTranslations` — they are unused.

## Features wiring

| Feature | Content file | Page |
|---------|--------------|------|
| Rules | `en\|zh/rules.md` | `games/[slug]/page.tsx` |
| Flow | **root** `flow.json` (bilingual; `startNode`, not `start`) | `…/flow/page.tsx` → `DecisionTree` |
| Score | `score.json` | `…/score/page.tsx` — dedicated trackers for `cabo-multi` / `sea-salt-multi` / `just-wild-multi`, else `ScoreTracker` + engines |
| Trainer | `trainer.json` | `…/trainer/page.tsx` + `src/lib/<domain>/` |
| Calculator | `calculator.json` | `…/calculator/page.tsx` |

Shared types live in `src/types/game.ts` (or domain `src/lib/<x>/`). Do not add a parallel `src/lib/content/types.ts`.

## UI

- Tokens from `src/app/globals.css` (`primary` / `accent` / `surface` / `border`, `font-heading`, `shadow-card`). No dark mode, no new palette unless asked.
- Category is `board` | `card` (not `party`). Layout rhythm: `mx-auto max-w-* px-4`, cards `rounded-2xl border-border bg-white shadow-card`.

## Red lines

- Changing `public/sw.js` or SW registration in `layout.tsx`: keep network-first for HTML/`/data/`; never break navigation fallbacks; do not auto-reload on **first** `controllerchange`.
- SEO helpers in `src/lib/seo.ts` + postbuild sitemap — preserve canonical/`basePath` paths when adding routes.
- Scope: only what the task needs; delete obsolete code when replacing a path; no drive-by refactors or unsolicited markdown docs.
